org.opendaylight.controller.switchmanager.internal

Class SwitchManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.switchmanager.internal.SwitchManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandProvider, IConfigurationAwareCommon, IConfigurationContainerAware, IListenInventoryUpdates, IObjectReader, ISwitchManager

    public class SwitchManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISwitchManager, IConfigurationContainerAware, IObjectReader, IListenInventoryUpdates, CommandProvider
    The class describes SwitchManager which is the central repository of all the inventory data including nodes, node connectors, properties attached, Layer3 configurations, Span configurations, node configurations, network device representations viewed by Controller Web applications. One SwitchManager instance per container of the network. All the node/nodeConnector properties are maintained in the default container only.
